theorem Topology.interior_closure_eq_univ_iff_closure_eq_univ
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    interior (closure A) = (Set.univ : Set X) ↔ closure A = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  constructor
  · intro hInt
    apply Set.Subset.antisymm
    · exact Set.Subset_univ _
    · intro x _
      have hx : x ∈ interior (closure A) := by
        simpa [hInt] using (by simp : x ∈ (Set.univ : Set X))
      exact interior_subset hx
  · intro hCl
    simpa [hCl, interior_univ]
